- **X** is launching **AI Note Writers** to help create Community Notes on posts.
- These AI bots will only contribute when **requested** and will be **marked clearly**; their help is judged by **public helpfulness**.
- The initiative aims to **increase note production** with **human oversight** to ensure the **quality and reliability** of information.

